{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001924", "chronotag": "1757948812265", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "1924", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1924", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC1364", "triAmendement": "ecaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaui", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA722374", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845454", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Isaac-Sibille"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 10", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 10", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 10", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1364.asp#D_Article_10"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "2", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 2"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;&#x00C0; l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;2, substituer aux mots&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;d&#x2019;aide&nbsp;&#x00BB;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">les mots&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;de droit&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">II.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;En cons&#x00E9;quence, &#x00E0; l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;3, substituer aux mots&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;&#x00E0; l&#x2019;aide&nbsp;&#x00BB;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">les mots&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;au droit&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">III.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;En cons&#x00E9;quence, &#x00E0; la premi&#x00E8;re phrase de l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;4, substituer aux mots&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;d&#x2019;aide&nbsp;&#x00BB;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">les mots&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;de droit&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement vise &#x00E0; renommer l&#x2019;aide &#x00E0; mourir en &#x00AB; droit &#x00E0; mourir &#x00BB;.&nbsp;</p><p><br>L&#x2019;objectif de cet amendement est de nommer les choses avec clart&#x00E9;, transparence et sinc&#x00E9;rit&#x00E9; &#x00E0; l&#x2019;&#x00E9;gard de nos concitoyens. Cette proposition de loi vise &#x00E0; cr&#x00E9;er un droit &#x00E0; mourir, qui constitue une entorse encadr&#x00E9;e au droit &#x00E0; la vie, tel qu&#x2019;il est consacr&#x00E9; par l&#x2019;article 3 de la D&#x00E9;claration universelle des droits de l&#x2019;Homme et au sein de la&nbsp; Convention de sauvegarde des droits de l'homme et des libert&#x00E9;s fondamentales.</p><p><br>Cette d&#x00E9;rogation est strictement limit&#x00E9;e aux cas de maladies graves et incurables causant des souffrances insupportables que la m&#x00E9;decine ne parvient plus &#x00E0; soulager.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-05-09", "datePublication": "2025-05-23", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Non soutenu"}}, "dateSort": "2025-05-23T15:16:10+02:00", "sort": "Non soutenu"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001924?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": "RUANR5L17S2025IDS29399", "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "1", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "30878", "typePosition": "Premier"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}